to that there was no thought.

00:25:37.235 --> 00:25:38.337 align:middle line:90%
It's almost just witnessing.

00:25:38.337 --> 00:25:39.871 align:middle line:84%
I would just be witnessing
my breath.

00:25:39.871 --> 00:25:41.974 align:middle line:84%
And all of a sudden I
say you have between 12

00:25:41.974 --> 00:25:44.109 align:middle line:90%
