not-- I try to like stop.

00:25:50.882 --> 00:25:51.883 align:middle line:90%
I try to get rid of--

00:25:51.883 --> 00:25:53.251 align:middle line:84%
>> Regina: But somehow
it didn't work

00:25:53.251 --> 00:25:54.286 align:middle line:84%
>> Martin: Nothing,
it wouldn't work.

00:25:54.286 --> 00:25:55.921 align:middle line:90%
It wouldn't work.

00:25:55.921 --> 00:26:00.158 align:middle line:84%
I was supposed to transfer into
the University of Florida now

00:26:00.158 --> 00:26:03.895 align:middle line:84%
