these two experiences.

00:26:06.131 --> 00:26:08.100 align:middle line:84%
I was like who needs
to go out of college,

00:26:08.100 --> 00:26:09.868 align:middle line:84%
that's like the most
insane thing,

00:26:09.868 --> 00:26:11.536 align:middle line:90%
but I hightailed it out Florida.

00:26:11.536 --> 00:26:14.906 align:middle line:84%
I went back to work at the baker
with my dad and so I was like,

00:26:14.906 --> 00:26:17.676 align:middle line:84%
so I wanted some sort of
normalcy, I was just grabbing

00:26:17.676 --> 00:26:21.279 align:middle line:84%
out straws and I went back
there and I was terrified.

00:26:21.279 --> 00:26:25.250 align:middle line:84%
