00:26:36.428 --> 00:26:37.696 align:middle line:90%
>> Regina: He was, yeah.

00:26:37.696 --> 00:26:38.830 align:middle line:84%
>> Martin: You know, they
always envisioned Cheever

00:26:38.830 --> 00:26:39.898 align:middle line:84%
as the Keller [assumed
spelling].

00:26:39.898 --> 00:26:41.266 align:middle line:90%
>> Regina: Right.

00:26:41.266 --> 00:26:42.200 align:middle line:84%
>> Martin: So, I thought, you
