I said, "That's my guru."

00:27:12.164 --> 00:27:12.798 align:middle line:90%
They go, "Yeah, right."

00:27:12.798 --> 00:27:13.765 align:middle line:90%
>> Regina: Right.

00:27:13.765 --> 00:27:14.866 align:middle line:84%
>> Martin: You know,
it's like crazy.

00:27:14.866 --> 00:27:16.702 align:middle line:84%
It's like, this guy
