00:27:25.577 --> 00:27:26.411 align:middle line:90%
>> Martin: Exactly.

00:27:26.411 --> 00:27:27.379 align:middle line:90%
>> Regina: -- that connection

00:27:27.379 --> 00:27:28.580 align:middle line:84%
with the divine aspect
of yourself.

00:27:28.580 --> 00:27:29.915 align:middle line:90%
>> Martin: Oh totally, totally.

