00:27:41.326 --> 00:27:42.694 align:middle line:84%
you ended up going
to Ashram [phonetic].

00:27:42.694 --> 00:27:43.762 align:middle line:90%
It was in Oakland?

00:27:43.762 --> 00:27:44.563 align:middle line:84%
>> Martin: It was
Oakland, that's right.

00:27:44.563 --> 00:27:45.397 align:middle line:90%
>> Regina: Yeah.

00:27:45.397 --> 00:27:46.932 align:middle line:90%
>> Martin: It was in Oakland.

00:27:46.932 --> 00:27:49.701 align:middle line:84%
I went out there and I was
like the funny thing was it's

00:27:49.701 --> 00:27:52.738 align:middle line:84%
like now it's like so
repentant that I was on--

00:27:52.738 --> 00:27:56.074 align:middle line:84%
At first I will do anything
the guru tells me to do

00:27:56.074 --> 00:27:58.043 align:middle line:84%
and I got three days
off with my dad.

00:27:58.043 --> 00:28:00.378 align:middle line:84%
I said I'm flying out to
California, all right.

00:28:00.378 --> 00:28:02.047 align:middle line:84%
I was just going to
go out and come back

00:28:02.047 --> 00:28:03.882 align:middle line:90%
and then go back out again.

00:28:03.882 --> 00:28:05.517 align:middle line:90%
So I have my private meeting.

00:28:05.517 --> 00:28:08.019 align:middle line:84%
This is the first time
I physically meeting him

00:28:08.019 --> 00:28:09.621 align:middle line:84%
and he's sitting
in there, so the--

00:28:09.621 --> 00:28:11.356 align:middle line:84%
