00:28:16.528 --> 00:28:17.796 align:middle line:90%
What do you want me to do?"

00:28:17.796 --> 00:28:19.164 align:middle line:84%
And he's like laughed, he
goes, "Stay this weekend."

00:28:19.164 --> 00:28:20.465 align:middle line:84%
He's like, hitting
me this teacup.

00:28:20.465 --> 00:28:21.666 align:middle line:84%
