00:28:25.837 --> 00:28:27.139 align:middle line:90%
come back.

00:28:27.139 --> 00:28:28.607 align:middle line:84%
You know, I said, "No, I'm
not going to-- I can't stay.

00:28:28.607 --> 00:28:31.576 align:middle line:84%
I said to Baba, I can't stay
but I'll end up coming back

00:28:31.576 --> 00:28:34.179 align:middle line:84%
but then when-- he just left the
room and he was like laughing

00:28:34.179 --> 00:28:37.215 align:middle line:84%
and laughing and laughing like
he was just reading my mind,

00:28:37.215 --> 00:28:39.084 align:middle line:90%
knowing I'm trying to surrender

00:28:39.084 --> 00:28:40.585 align:middle line:84%
and I can't do the
simplest thing

00:28:40.585 --> 00:28:42.554 align:middle line:84%
that he's telling
me to do, you know?

00:28:42.554 --> 00:28:43.955 align:middle line:90%
>> Regina: Yeah.

00:28:43.955 --> 00:28:45.590 align:middle line:84%
>> Martin: And of course, in the
flight back, I'm beating myself

00:28:45.590 --> 00:28:47.092 align:middle line:84%
up again like I waited
all this time

00:28:47.092 --> 00:28:49.795 align:middle line:84%
and I can't follow the guy
instructions, you know?

00:28:49.795 --> 00:28:53.498 align:middle line:84%
But then I did end up going out,
so I live there for six month

00:28:53.498 --> 00:28:56.101 align:middle line:84%
and just have like-- it
was amazing because--

00:28:56.101 --> 00:28:57.969 align:middle line:84%
>> Regina: Well, and you ended
up in an interesting position.

00:28:57.969 --> 00:29:02.040 align:middle line:84%
There seem to be a connection
between the two of you, right?

00:29:02.040 --> 00:29:03.909 align:middle line:84%
Kind of ended that--
you ended up closer

00:29:03.909 --> 00:29:05.310 align:middle line:90%
than most people do to a guru.

00:29:05.310 --> 00:29:07.946 align:middle line:84%
>> Martin: Well, the thing was
because of my bakery experience,

00:29:07.946 --> 00:29:10.482 align:middle line:84%
they put me in this tiny
little armor which is really

00:29:10.482 --> 00:29:11.817 align:middle line:90%
about the size of the stature.

00:29:11.817 --> 00:29:14.686 align:middle line:84%
It's very, very small, you
know, it had like three tables

00:29:14.686 --> 00:29:18.523 align:middle line:84%
and there might be five or
six stools and there was maybe

00:29:18.523 --> 00:29:20.992 align:middle line:84%
