living in the Ashram at the time

00:29:20.992 --> 00:29:22.794 align:middle line:84%
and they had-- we're
having programs and--

00:29:22.794 --> 00:29:24.129 align:middle line:84%
the programs are
wild 'cause it was

00:29:24.129 --> 00:29:26.198 align:middle line:84%
like crazy kundalini
experiences.

00:29:26.198 --> 00:29:29.935 align:middle line:84%
People were like, you know, it
sounded like a jungle literally/

00:29:29.935 --> 00:29:31.002 align:middle line:90%
>> Regina: Yeah.

00:29:31.002 --> 00:29:32.270 align:middle line:84%
>> Martin: And people
are flying into--

00:29:32.270 --> 00:29:33.738 align:middle line:84%
I mean Muktananda would go
around and touch everybody

00:29:33.738 --> 00:29:36.474 align:middle line:84%
and just like light them
up like it was unreal,

00:29:36.474 --> 00:29:38.009 align:middle line:84%
and I was having a lot
of Kundalini experience,

00:29:38.009 --> 00:29:39.611 align:middle line:84%
but for the most part
I was like working.

00:29:39.611 --> 00:29:43.114 align:middle line:84%
I was living their full time
in this little place, you know?

00:29:43.114 --> 00:29:45.417 align:middle line:84%
And I had a number of
interaction with him

00:29:45.417 --> 00:29:46.651 align:middle line:90%
which were kind of funny.

00:29:46.651 --> 00:29:48.353 align:middle line:84%
One night he basically
was looking

00:29:48.353 --> 00:29:51.022 align:middle line:84%
for the person who's running
the place and he was looking

00:29:51.022 --> 00:29:52.824 align:middle line:84%
in from the outside of
the window in the dark

00:29:52.824 --> 00:29:54.926 align:middle line:84%
and I thought it was-- it was
in the bad section of Oakland

00:29:54.926 --> 00:29:57.062 align:middle line:84%
and they thought, I thought
somebody was robbing us

00:29:57.062 --> 00:29:58.997 align:middle line:84%
so I got a baseball
bat and I was like,

00:29:58.997 --> 00:30:00.799 align:middle line:84%
going over to the door,
opening the door like I'm going

00:30:00.799 --> 00:30:02.801 align:middle line:84%
to hit this guy,
it's Muktananda.

00:30:02.801 --> 00:30:04.870 align:middle line:84%
With no teeth coming
in like that,

