00:53:14.825 --> 00:53:16.927 align:middle line:84%
in because there was
a big, heavy door.

00:53:16.927 --> 00:53:19.263 align:middle line:84%
And, you know, I'm trying to get
in and there's a homeless guy

00:53:19.263 --> 00:53:23.033 align:middle line:84%
that comes down kind of a big--
you know, bag of cans, you know,

00:53:23.033 --> 00:53:25.402 align:middle line:84%
and a garbage bag,
and just hasn't been--

00:53:25.402 --> 00:53:27.704 align:middle line:84%
had a bath like in a year or
something like that, you know,

00:53:27.704 --> 00:53:31.241 align:middle line:84%
and he looks at me with
such love, and compassion,

00:53:31.241 --> 00:53:34.645 align:middle line:84%
and goes over and
opens the door for me.

00:53:34.645 --> 00:53:37.014 align:middle line:84%
And as I go in, pushed the
button to the elevator,

00:53:37.014 --> 00:53:40.450 align:middle line:84%
soon as I get in the elevator,
boom, I'm just like bowling.

00:53:40.450 --> 00:53:43.153 align:middle line:84%
You know, I am crying
and crying--

00:53:43.153 --> 00:53:46.323 align:middle line:84%
it's like this emotional
outburst I couldn't figure out.

00:53:46.323 --> 00:53:49.960 align:middle line:84%
So next-- you know, afternoon,
I walked out of my balcony,

00:53:49.960 --> 00:53:51.361 align:middle line:90%
the same type of thing happens.

00:53:51.361 --> 00:53:53.397 align:middle line:84%
So people upstairs although I
don't know, are yelling down,

00:53:53.397 --> 00:53:55.999 align:middle line:90%
"Hey, do you need any help?

00:53:55.999 --> 00:53:57.734 align:middle line:84%
Do you want us to
get you anything?"

00:53:57.734 --> 00:54:00.070 align:middle line:90%
you know, and I'd say--

00:54:00.070 --> 00:54:01.471 align:middle line:84%
>> Regina: So you had
to learn the humility

00:54:01.471 --> 00:54:02.406 align:middle line:90%
that you're receiving.

00:54:02.406 --> 00:54:03.307 align:middle line:84%
>> Martin: Yeah,
I had to receive.

00:54:03.307 --> 00:54:04.341 align:middle line:90%
I had never received in my life.

00:54:04.341 --> 00:54:05.575 align:middle line:90%
>> Regina: Yeah, right.

00:54:05.575 --> 00:54:07.010 align:middle line:84%
>> Martin: So I started
meditating and I was trying

00:54:07.010 --> 00:54:09.780 align:middle line:84%
to figure out what the
heck-- what was going on?

00:54:09.780 --> 00:54:13.350 align:middle line:84%
And I-- I kept on seeing myself
as a two years old in a crib.

00:54:13.350 --> 00:54:14.718 align:middle line:84%
And my mother saying,
"Marty, put your head

00:54:14.718 --> 00:54:15.852 align:middle line:90%
down and go to sleep."

00:54:15.852 --> 00:54:17.921 align:middle line:84%
And I realized that I
started holding a belief

00:54:17.921 --> 00:54:20.190 align:middle line:90%
that I wasn't lovable, OK,

00:54:20.190 --> 00:54:23.560 align:middle line:84%
from the time I was
really, really young.

00:54:23.560 --> 00:54:25.796 align:middle line:84%
>> Regina: And here, all
these people are now coming

00:54:25.796 --> 00:54:29.399 align:middle line:84%
to your aid, they're loving
you, the final piece you needed

00:54:29.399 --> 00:54:30.967 align:middle line:84%
in order to find
what you wanted.

00:54:30.967 --> 00:54:32.269 align:middle line:84%
>> Martin: That's
right, that's right.

00:54:32.269 --> 00:54:36.206 align:middle line:84%
So-- and then I go out into
the hallway and I'm going

00:54:36.206 --> 00:54:38.208 align:middle line:84%
down the hall, some guy
gets off the elevator

00:54:38.208 --> 00:54:40.310 align:middle line:84%
and because I have
this new understanding

00:54:40.310 --> 00:54:44.381 align:middle line:84%
without the thought I'm not
lovable and it was just light.

00:54:44.381 --> 00:54:46.616 align:middle line:84%
I felt like Jesus
was coming down

00:54:46.616 --> 00:54:49.486 align:middle line:84%
and I just could not take the
feel that's why really the name

00:54:49.486 --> 00:54:50.654 align:middle line:84%
