love comes from is

00:54:50.654 --> 00:54:53.724 align:middle line:84%
like that field is
always there all the time.

00:54:53.724 --> 00:54:54.491 align:middle line:90%
>> Regina: All of the time--

00:54:54.491 --> 00:54:55.692 align:middle line:90%
>> Martin: All the time.

00:54:55.692 --> 00:54:57.961 align:middle line:84%
We can just open ourselves
to and not, you know,

00:54:57.961 --> 00:54:59.830 align:middle line:90%
and not get in the way.

00:54:59.830 --> 00:55:00.964 align:middle line:90%
So--

00:55:00.964 --> 00:55:01.631 align:middle line:84%
>> Regina: Well, we have
