00:55:01.631 --> 00:55:02.466 align:middle line:90%
>> Martin: Yeah, OK.

00:55:02.466 --> 00:55:03.533 align:middle line:90%
>> Regina: Any final thought--

00:55:03.533 --> 00:55:04.735 align:middle line:84%
