one of these kind

00:55:04.735 --> 00:55:06.937 align:middle line:84%
of explosive beautiful
experiences after another.

00:55:06.937 --> 00:55:07.771 align:middle line:90%
>> Martin: Yeah.

00:55:07.771 --> 00:55:08.805 align:middle line:90%
>> Regina: So just in a minute,

00:55:08.805 --> 00:55:10.707 align:middle line:84%
