00:55:16.279 --> 00:55:20.050 align:middle line:84%
That everything that was
going on is just movement.

00:55:20.050 --> 00:55:22.686 align:middle line:84%
It seems that we're sort
of in control of the doer

00:55:22.686 --> 00:55:26.156 align:middle line:84%
